/* ============================================================ */
/* IMPORTANT: MATCH FIGMA VARIABLE NAMES                        */
/* ============================================================ */
/* 
   Make sure the font-family names you use here EXACTLY match
   the font-family names in your Figma variables.
   
   For example, if your Figma variable uses:
     font-family: "Playfair Display"
   
   Then your Google Fonts import or @font-face must define
   that exact name: 'Playfair Display'
   
   The build process will automatically add fallback system fonts,
   so you only need to define the primary font name.
*/